        {
            "title": "分析師:三星2027年前全部記憶體晶片產能預計售罄",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qrLfpDVeT_YXZ61lumkxXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7R04R_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 據KB Securities分析師Jeff Kim表示,三星電子(Samsung Electronics)正進入全面盈利增長期,其2027年前的全部記憶體晶片供應可能售罄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kim在週四的報告中指出,人工智慧需求激增以及行業供應增長有限,預計將使DRAM和NAND市場在未來數年保持緊張狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kim寫道,「三星電子2027年前的全部記憶體產能預計將售罄」,並補充說主要科技公司現在「越來越多地考慮簽訂5年期(-2030年)供應商協議」以確保供應。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0c7b2145-8daf-3f5e-89a6-3c6c654288cd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場趨緊促使該公司將三星的目標價上調33%至320,000韓元,反映出盈利預測大幅上調。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kim指出,2026年營業利潤預估已上調30%至220萬億韓元,2027年預估上調57%至301萬億韓元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">記憶體價格是看漲前景的核心。KB Securities現預計2026年DRAM價格將年增148%,NAND價格將年增111%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告稱:「隨著需求急劇增加,供應增長可能在2027年前保持受限,DRAM/NAND價格預計將維持上漲軌跡。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期前景也更為強勁。Kim預測「2026年第一季營業利潤為40萬億韓元(年增5倍,季增2倍)」,受記憶體利潤率飆升推動,僅記憶體部門預計將產生38萬億韓元營業利潤,僅一個季度就超過2025年全年總盈利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著AI模型從基於文本的系統轉向整合視覺、語言和行為的多模態架構,KB Securities預計來自機器人和自動駕駛汽車等邊緣AI設備的需求將在未來十年內強化「記憶體晶片需求的結構性增長」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB-%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F2027%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E9%AB%94%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E7%94%A2%E8%83%BD%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E5%94%AE%E7%BD%84-175150962.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 02:13:12",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "本田重整電動車野心,麥格理稱公司「面臨現實考驗」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r6z5ITcy3iQJv0HcKwnoHQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEC9U0AR_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 本田正在進行<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"麥格理\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:麥格理;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/麥格理\">麥格理</a>所稱的全面「戰略重整」,調整其電動車野心,這引發了大幅盈利下調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師James Hong表示,本田修訂後的指引反映出該公司承認「先前以電動車為主導的投資計劃已不再獲得市場現實的支持」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據麥格理的報告,本田目前預計2026財年3月期將出現2,700億至5,700億日圓的營業虧損,這與先前預測的5,500億日圓利潤形成逆轉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這意味著業績惡化了8,200億至1.12萬億日圓。淨利潤指引也從預期的3,000億日圓利潤下調至4,200億至6,900億日圓虧損,主要是由於取消了其美國電動車項目,包括Honda 0 Series和Acura RSX。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2f730893-b409-3b82-8ae9-c21c56bded9e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hong指出,這些舉措將產生「8,200億至1.12萬億日圓的額外營業費用」,加上與減記、資產減值和項目取消相關的「1,100億至1,500億日圓的權益法損失」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">麥格理估計,總計2.5萬億日圓損失中約有1.3萬億日圓將在本財年入賬,其餘1.2萬億日圓將在2027財年3月期消化。儘管面臨動盪,本田仍將維持股息,麥格理表示這應有助於支撐估值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hong指出,此次重整反映了美國電動車需求放緩、影響內燃機和混合動力車經濟效益的政策轉變,以及來自中國本土電動車製造商在軟件和ADAS功能方面更強競爭力的加劇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本田的復甦現在取決於混合動力車的執行情況。麥格理寫道,中期表現將取決於該汽車製造商能否「通過HEV擴張和降低固定成本重建四輪車業務盈利能力」,同時優先發展日本、美國和印度市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">麥格理維持中性評級,稱本田為其「日本汽車股中最不看好的標的」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B0%E9%87%8D%E6%95%B4%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%87%8E%E5%BF%83-%E9%BA%A5%E6%A0%BC%E7%90%86%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6%E8%80%83%E9%A9%97-171903903.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 02:13:14",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國抵押貸款利率創11個月來最大漲幅 伊朗戰爭引發通膨憂慮",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國抵押貸款利率創近一年來最大漲幅，伊朗戰爭引發的通膨擔憂給即將到來的春季銷售季增添了不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">房地美周四公佈的數據顯示，30年期固定利率抵押貸款的平均利率從上周的6%升至6.11%，為2025年4月以來最大單周升幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利率在2月底短暫跌破6%，疊加房價趨於平穩，市場原本對春季銷售季略有改善抱有期待。但如果戰爭持續，油價可能進一步上漲，這將推高通膨並繼續對引導房貸利率走勢的美國國債殖利率施加上行壓力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-60852fc1-595f-3a0d-9bbd-eb3e281479ec-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，與一年前相比，借貸成本仍明顯下降，當時30年期平均利率為6.65%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bright MLS首席經濟學家Lisa Sturtevant表示：「今年春季市場活動前景已不及一個月前利率下行時的水平。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Mortgage Rates Jump Most in 11 Months on War Inflation Risk</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B511%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE-162533121.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 01:06:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美銀:加拿大央行料在地緣政治波動中維持利率不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x.NqXbTGlHvwtOqJIz8Wgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/moved_LYNXMPEL3F0OD_L.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國銀行證券(BofA Securities)經濟學家Carlos Capistran在報告中指出,加拿大央行預計將在2026年全年維持政策利率在2.25%。持續的地緣政治緊張局勢和貿易不確定性預計將使央行維持當前立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗軍事行動後能源市場飆升,為加拿大經濟前景帶來顯著的上行風險。Capistran就經濟順風的轉變表示:\"油價上漲會推動加拿大的經濟增長和通脹,因此不利於降息。\"</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-40a74863-2cce-3980-8c19-13105eb21b6c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管加拿大國內經濟在2025年末出現GDP收縮,顯示經濟疲軟,但原油價格飆升起到了結構性對沖作用。美銀認為,央行將在即將發布的前瞻指引中採取謹慎基調,以保持政策靈活性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勞動力市場在1月份表現參差不齊,也為政策制定者帶來複雜局面。Capistran指出:\"失業率降至6.5%,但這是由勞動力參與率下降推動的,而非真正的就業增長。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通脹動態進一步使未來路徑複雜化,核心指標持續向目標下行。然而,美銀警告稱,油價持續上漲10%可能使整體通脹率提高約40個點子。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場定價已開始反映這種鷹派轉變,偏離了先前對利率寬鬆的預期。Capistran寫道:\"加拿大經濟通常受益於油價上漲,我們現在認為風險平衡正從2026年加拿大央行降息轉向潛在加息。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
